IELTS Speaking application is MVVM based Android-kotlin app.
This app target  those who are preparing for study abroad and want to improve their english communication skill.
App use google's TTS engine as Prime AI in the app.
Prime AI will ask questions based on CountDown Timer and user need to answer the questions
Whole Conversation will store in .mp3 format so user can listne their audio recording and find their own mistake.
This application alo include PRIME USER LOGIN. which include some additional feature and users have two option
BUY PREMIUM DIRECTLY FROM APP or you can join any IELTS tuition classes inside INDIA and if your TUITION is not register then let us know 
so we will add your classes into app firebase realtime database, by this way user can unlock all premium feature in FREE OF COST.
